articles.description: Daniel Utomi had 26 points and Freshman Virshon Cotton scored five of his 21 points in the final 45 seconds to help Akron beat Western Michigan 79-78 on Monday night in the Mid-American Conference Tournament.
articles.headline: Cotton helps Akron beat Western Michigan in MAC tourney

articles.headline: Northeastern cruises past UNC Wilmington 79-52
